d with insulin, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/191626/', '', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', '', 1767369485);
